                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="welcome-card">
                <h3 style="color: #667eea; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Important Instructions</h3>
                <ul style="text-align: left; color: #666; line-height: 1.8;">
                    <li>Once you start the test, you must complete it within 60 minutes</li>
